#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.233"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.233:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:0.2"
msgid "24. Āvāsikavagga "
msgstr "24. A Resident Mendicant "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.233:0.3"
msgid "233. Sobhanasutta "
msgstr "233. Beautification "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.263, sc1
msgctxt "an5.233:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu āvāsaṃ sobheti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a resident mendicant with five qualities beautifies the monastery. "

msgctxt "an5.233:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:1.3"
msgid "Sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu; "
msgstr "They’re ethical, restrained in the code of conduct, with good behavior and supporters. Seeing danger in the slightest fault, they keep the rules they’ve undertaken. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:1.4"
msgid "bahussuto hoti … pe … diṭṭhiyā suppaṭividdhā; "
msgstr "They’re very learned, remembering and keeping what they’ve learned. These teachings are good in the beginning, good in the middle, and good in the end, meaningful and well-phrased, describing a spiritual practice that’s totally full and pure. They are very learned in such teachings, remembering them, reciting them, mentally scrutinizing them, and understanding them with right view. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:1.5"
msgid "kalyāṇavāco hoti kalyāṇavākkaraṇo poriyā vācāya samannāgato vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā; "
msgstr "They’re a good speaker, with a polished, clear, and articulate voice that expresses the meaning. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:1.6"
msgid "paṭibalo hoti upasaṅkamante dhammiyā kathāya sandassetuṃ samādapetuṃ samuttejetuṃ sampahaṃsetuṃ; "
msgstr "They’re able to educate, encourage, fire up, and inspire those who approach them with a Dhamma talk. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:1.7"
msgid "catunnaṃ jhānānaṃ ābhicetasikānaṃ diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārānaṃ nikāmalābhī hoti akicchalābhī akasiralābhī. "
msgstr "They get the four absorptions—blissful meditations in the present life that belong to the higher mind—when they want, without trouble or difficulty. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.233:1.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu āvāsaṃ sobhetī”ti. "
msgstr "A resident mendicant with these five qualities beautifies the monastery.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.233:1.9"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

